title: Pasjača (mountain)
text: Pasjača (<a href="Serbian%20Cyrillic">Serbian Cyrillic</a>: Пасјача) is a <a href="mountains%20of%20Serbia">mountain</a> in southern <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>, near the town of <a href="%C5%BDitora%C4%91a">Žitorađa</a>. Its highest peak has an elevation of 971 meters above sea level.
